data.description: A cant miss in one of the most sought after communities in DFW. Highly coveted Light farms in exemplarary Prosper ISD! This home is loaded with chic upgrades and is an entertainers dream! Exterior finished with german smear brick, Austin chalk stone and freshly painted trim.  Rare double lot backyard oasis outfitted with turf, putting green and new sparkling pool! This community includes miles of trails, five pools, tennis courts, a gym, private lake, and onsite restaurant.
